│       ├── security-design-report.md  #   Security review (design phase)
│       ├── security-impl-report.md    #   Security review (implementation phase)
│       ├── bug-analysis.md        #   Bug analysis (bug pipeline only)
│       ├── {phase}-completeness.md #  Completeness review per phase
│       └── digests/               #   Phase digests (compact summaries for downstream agents)
│           └── {phase}-digest.md  #     e.g., design-digest.md, unit-test-digest.md, implement-digest.md
├── project/                       # Project management artifacts
