.claude/skills/sdd-shared/segments/
├── error-handling.md                # Error handling and retry logic
├── git-pr.md                        # Git commit, push, and PR creation (routes to provider segments)
├── github-repo.md                   # GitHub PR operations via gh CLI
├── bitbucket-repo.md                # Bitbucket PR operations via MCP tools
